data.description: Located in a beloved area, east of US1, this CBS home is waiting for you to make it your own. The owner's have recently tackled all the costly and practical home improvements. Now you get to do the fun part; designing the interior and making it your own! NEW ROOF, gutters and skylight in 2023, new A/C in 2021, new water heater in 2020.The guest bath and second and third bedrooms were recently redone. Kitchen-centric floor plan with pass through to patio makes this is the essential floor plan for entertaining! Additional features include a whole house GE water filter system,  cabana bath,  a fully fenced yard, split plan and more. Close to beach, shopping, dining, hospital, parks and schools.  Less than 2 hrs to Orlando & Miami. You simply must come and envision this home's full potential.
